Description: Al-Shabaab senior military commander; principal coordinator of al-Shabaab's militia attacks in Somalia, Kenya, and Uganda; head of the Amniyat, al-Shabaab's Security and Intelligence Branch.
Dhoore helped facilitate a deadly Christmas Day 2014 attack at the airport and a March 2015 attack at the Maka al-Mukarramah hotel.
Deputy commander for Lower Juba and senior military commander

Leaders Killed: Mohamed Sakr, Abu Ibrahim, and Akram
Aden Hashi Ayro and Sheikh Muhidin Mohamud Omar
